+//! Real-world use case: ML feature transformations for training/inference
+//!
+//! Operations tested:
+//!   1. Normalization (min-max, z-score)
+//!   2. One-hot encoding
+//!   3. Feature crossing
+//!   4. Binning/Bucketing
+//!   5. Log/Power transforms
+//!   6. Rolling window features
